description:
If you're looking for a fun, gospel-inspired karaoke experience, look no further than "Tenderly Calling." This karaoke bar features top-quality recordings of some of your favorite gospel songs, making it the perfect place to have some fun and belt out some tunes.

Motion Graphics Used : Gospel Productions by Joe Hackney
